Instantiation.name: HumbleSelf - (SS6 Act-3) Monica explains how she almost got caught stealing.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %greeting% %r%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Hey %i%. That's a pretty cool top you have.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Yeah, I stole it from the Mariano store at the Easthouse Mall. After I walked out with it the cashier ran after me.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Really?! What happened?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: I actually dropped my phone in the store as I was leaving and he ran after me to give it back.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Wow, that must have been scary.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: I wasn't worried about it. I was just lucky he didn't see the top.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: One day I want to steal a top and be just like you.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %r%, I'm glad I ran into you!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh, hey %i% what's up?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: I just wanted to let you know that, contrary to what you may have been led to believe...
I'm not a hero.
Just a %gender(i,man,woman)%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Okay... thanks for passing that along.
For what its worth, I've never really considered you a hero.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %r%, I'm glad I ran into you!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Hey %i%! How's everybody's favorite rock star?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: That's what I wanted to talk to you about. Look, contrary to what you may think...
I'm not a hero.
Just a %gender(i,man,woman)%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Whatever... You're the greatest %gender(i,guy,girl)% I know!

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: No... but...

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hey %r%.

I mean, remember when %toc1%?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Yeah, that was great. And I mean it's not like you've done anything that cool lately.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: It's true. I'm like a candle before the supernova of %op% coolness.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Why would anyone ever make one-way streets!? They're so annoying!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Wow! I would have never thought of that! You're so smart...

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: It was nothing, really.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: You're so modest!

Instantiation.name: HumbleSelf - Status: Annoyed with (r, i) Accept

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %r%! %r%! I have to tell you something important.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: What is it? Make it quick, I'm kind of annoyed with you.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Yeah, it was nothing really. I mean, I just heard that someone thinks that you think I'm cool. And you should know, I'm really not.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: That's rapidly not becoming a problem, %i%. You know what really bugs me, though? How much you belittle yourself.
It's really getting annoying... And it's certainly not cool.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Oh... Yeah, sorry. Totally not cool. I'm sorry.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: And stop apologizing all the time!

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %r%! %r%, is it truly you, or some other apparition sent to haunt my dreams!

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Of course its me, %i%.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Tell me, what week is it?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Why, Prom Week.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Ah, the Spirits have done it all in one week!
%r%... %o%... I, I'm sorry.

Will you please take me back, %o%?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: I have, %o%!
I've learned that I have a couple of really weird friends.
And that I wouldn't trade them for anyone in the world!

LineOfDialogue.otherLine: So, do you want to go do something later tonight?
